abstract: >-
  An AI system develops a geometrically precise internal number line
  purely from observing objects being gathered one at a time.
  No counting objective, no reward signal, no mathematical instruction.
  A DreamerV3 world model trained on next-state prediction
  spontaneously organizes its 512-dimensional hidden state into a
  1D manifold with correct topology, uniform spacing, and ordinal
  structure, verified through persistent homology, geodesic analysis,
  and representational similarity analysis. The counting manifold is
  robust across spatial arrangements, information ablations,
  observation scrambling, alternative architectures, and
  higher-dimensional worlds.
